        <h1>Loan Repayment Home </h1><br/>
			<table width="625px">
			<tr>
				<td><b>Pay Installments</b><br/>
					&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;After the Loan Id han been generated, student can pay the installment to NSEP in the Pay &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Installment menu. You need to enter Loan Id, Student Id, Amount and Date.<br/>
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><br/><b>View Installments</b><br/>
					&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You can view all the transaction details based on the Loan Id and the Student Id of a Student in a &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;tabular format.
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><br/><b>Update Installments</b><br/>
