				<td><br/><b>Generate Defaulter List</b><br/>
					&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;We can generate Defaulter List which contains list of students who has not paid the Installment before &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;the dead line i.e. 25th of each month and We can deduct that amount from that student's NSEP &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;account.
				</td>
			</tr>
